00:00:12.290 --> 00:00:15.910
<font color="#138ce9">MACE:</font> You refer to the prophecy of the
one who will bring balance to the Force.

3
00:00:17.410 --> 00:00:19.160
You believe it's this boy?

4
00:00:23.370 --> 00:00:26.620
Anakin Skywalker. meet Obi-Wan Kenobi.

5
00:00:28.410 --> 00:00:31.250
<font color="#138ce9">YODA:</font> <i>Clouded this boy's future is.</i>

6
00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:36.370
The boy is dangerous.
They all sense it. Why can't you?

7
00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:39.580
An apprentice you have. Qui-Gon.

8
00:00:39.660 --> 00:00:41.870
Impossible to take on a second.

9
00:00:41.950 --> 00:00:44.410
- Obi-Wan is ready.
- I am ready to face the trials.

10
00:00:50.250 --> 00:00:52.000
<font color="#138ce9">QUI-GON:</font> <i>You've been a good apprentice.
Obi-Wan.</i>

11
00:00:54.450 --> 00:00:56.160
No!

12
00:00:57.160 --> 00:00:59.290
<font color="#138ce9">QUI-GON:</font> <i>I foresee you will become
a great Jedi Knight.</i>

13
00:00:59.370 --> 00:01:00.830
Obi-Wan.

14
00:01:00.910 --> 00:01:02.910
Promise me you will train the boy.

15
00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:04.500
Yes. Master.

16
00:01:04.580 --> 00:01:08.000
He will bring balance.

17
00:01:08.410 --> 00:01:11.540
Master Yoda. I gave Qui-Gon my word.

18
00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:15.000
<font color="#138ce9">YODA:</font> <i>Your apprentice Skywalker will be.</i>

19
00:01:19.540 --> 00:01:20.540
What took you so long?

20
00:01:23.580 --> 00:01:25.250
<font color="#138ce9">ANAKIN:</font> <i>Obi-Wan is a great mentor.</i>

21
00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:27.500
<i>As wise as Master Yoda</i>

22
00:01:28.950 --> 00:01:30.870
<i>and as powerful as Master Windu.</i>

23
00:01:31.500 --> 00:01:33.790
<font color="#138ce9">PALPATINE:</font> You are the most gifted Jedi
I have ever met.

24
00:01:35.450 --> 00:01:38.330
<i>I see you becoming
the greatest of all the Jedi.</i>

25
00:01:39.660 --> 00:01:40.700
<font color="#138ce9">ANAKIN:</font> <i>I feel lost.</i>

26
00:01:41.830 --> 00:01:44.700
Lost? What do you mean?

27
00:01:44.790 --> 00:01:47.410
<font color="#138ce9">ANAKIN:</font> <i>I'm not the Jedi I should be.
I want more.</i>

28
00:01:48.080 --> 00:01:49.080
And I know I shouldn't.

29
00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:51.790
<i>How do you know the ways of the Force?</i>

30
00:01:52.870 --> 00:01:55.540
My mentor taught me everything
about the Force.

31
00:01:56.580 --> 00:01:59.290
Even the nature of the dark side

32
00:02:00.910 --> 00:02:02.500
Only through me

33
00:02:02.580 --> 00:02:06.200
can you achieve a power
greater than any Jedi.

34
00:02:06.410 --> 00:02:08.120
<font color="#ff00ff">(GASPING)</font> I can't.

35
00:02:08.580 --> 00:02:09.700
Don't give up. Padmé.

36
00:02:11.160 --> 00:02:13.330
<font color="#138ce9">PALPATINE:</font> <i>The power to save Padmé.</i>

37
00:02:14.080 --> 00:02:16.160
