212
00:18:29.700 --> 00:18:31.040
<font color="#ff00ff">(BREATHING HEAVILY)</font>

213
00:18:36.620 --> 00:18:39.580
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTS SOFTLY)</font>

214
00:18:41.000 --> 00:18:45.040
<font color="#ff00ff">(BREATHING HEAVILY)</font>

215
00:18:47.410 --> 00:18:48.500
Master Qui-Gon.

216
00:18:52.700 --> 00:18:53.790
Master?

217
00:18:58.830 --> 00:19:02.120
<font color="#ff00ff">(SIGHING)</font>

218
00:19:05.250 --> 00:19:07.120
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHITTERING)</font>

219
00:19:13.290 --> 00:19:15.290
<font color="#ff00ff">(EOPIE BELLOWING)</font>

220
00:19:38.330 --> 00:19:39.790
<font color="#ff00ff">(EOPIE GRUNTS)</font>

221
00:19:46.830 --> 00:19:49.500
<font color="#138ce9">OWEN:</font> Grab two of those canisters.

222
00:19:49.700 --> 00:19:51.000
<font color="#ff00ff">(WHIRRING)</font>

223
00:20:02.700 --> 00:20:03.790
Luke?

224
00:20:06.040 --> 00:20:07.160
<font color="#ff00ff">(WHIRS)</font>

225
00:20:08.750 --> 00:20:09.830
Luke!

226
00:20:10.660 --> 00:20:11.660
Luke!

227
00:20:11.750 --> 00:20:13.580
Did he go back inside?

228
00:20:13.660 --> 00:20:14.750
He's run off.

229
00:20:16.790 --> 00:20:17.870
Luke?

230
00:20:23.700 --> 00:20:24.790
<font color="#138ce9">BERU:</font> Luke?

231
00:20:29.750 --> 00:20:30.830
<font color="#138ce9">OWEN:</font> Luke?

232
00:20:33.870 --> 00:20:36.750
- <font color="#ff00ff">(PLAYFUL CHATTER)</font>
- <font color="#ff00ff">(BERU LAUGHS)</font>

233
00:21:14.120 --> 00:21:17.290
<font color="#ff00ff">(EOPIE GRUNTING)</font>

234
00:21:21.830 --> 00:21:24.290
<font color="#ff00ff">(RUSTLING)</font>

235
00:21:33.700 --> 00:21:36.750
<font color="#ff00ff">(SMALL ROCKS FALLING)</font>

236
00:21:40.160 --> 00:21:41.250
<font color="#138ce9">MAN:</font> Master.

237
00:21:42.660 --> 00:21:44.910
I thought I saw you in the town.
but I wasn't sure.

238
00:21:45.000 --> 00:21:46.540
I didn't think you'd survived.

239
00:21:46.620 --> 00:21:48.620
You're making some kind of mistake.

240
00:21:48.700 --> 00:21:50.250
I'm sorry. my name is Nari.

241
00:21:51.160 --> 00:21:52.200
Um. there's no mistake.

242
00:21:53.830 --> 00:21:55.540
You're looking for somebody else.

243
00:21:56.790 --> 00:21:58.200
What are you doing here. Obi-Wan?

244
00:21:58.290 --> 00:21:59.410
My name is Ben.

245
00:22:00.250 --> 00:22:01.330
<font color="#138ce9">NARI:</font> Come on. please.

246
00:22:01.830 --> 00:22:02.910
Please.

247
00:22:04.500 --> 00:22:06.330
You have no idea what I've been through.

248
00:22:20.000 --> 00:22:21.160
You must leave.

249
00:22:22.080 --> 00:22:23.370
You'll draw too much attention.

250
00:22:23.450 --> 00:22:24.750
But I have nowhere to go.

251
00:22:24.830 --> 00:22:27.200
They're hunting me. You have to help me.

252
00:22:28.750 --> 00:22:29.830
You want my help?

253
00:22:30.290 --> 00:22:31.370
Take this.

254
00:22:31.870 --> 00:22:34.700
Walk into the middle of the desert
and bury it in the ground.

255
00:22:37.410 --> 00:22:38.410
Stay hidden.

256
00:22:40.200 --> 00:22:41.200
Live a normal life.

257
00:22:41.290 --> 00:22:44.120
What about the people that need us?
What about the fight?

258
00:22:45.450 --> 00:22:46.620
The fight is done.

259
00:22:47.500 --> 00:22:48.580
We lost.

260
00:22:51.040 --> 00:22:52.120
What happened to you?

261
00:22:54.160 --> 00:22:55.660
You were once a great Jedi.

262
00:22:58.750 --> 00:23:00.830
The time of the Jedi is over.

263
00:23:06.290 --> 00:23:07.580
Go back to the town.

264
00:23:08.790 --> 00:23:09.870
Let it go.

265
00:23:55.200 --> 00:23:56.660
We're going to be late.

266
00:23:56.750 --> 00:23:58.620
Come on. let's hurry it along.

267
00:23:58.700 --> 00:23:59.700
How is she doing?

268
00:23:59.790 --> 00:24:00.790
She's ready?

269
00:24:01.370 --> 00:24:02.450
Great.

270
00:24:03.080 --> 00:24:04.330
Thank you.

271
00:24:04.410 --> 00:24:06.870
Remember.
my sister's whole family is coming.

272
00:24:07.370 --> 00:24:08.660
We need their support.

273
00:24:08.750 --> 00:24:10.330
So try not to make anyone cry.

274
00:24:10.410 --> 00:24:12.870
There will be sweetmallows
at the reception after.

275
00:24:13.580 --> 00:24:16.000
If you behave. I will let you...

276
00:24:21.870 --> 00:24:24.660
She insisted
you would find it amusing. Your Highness.

277
00:24:29.750 --> 00:24:32.000
She's either in the cellar.
in the kitchen...

278
00:24:32.830 --> 00:24:34.540
<font color="#ff00ff">(SIGHS)</font> ...or in the woods.

279
00:24:40.370 --> 00:24:41.830
<font color="#ff00ff">(DROID CHIRPING)</font>

280
00:25:11.330 --> 00:25:13.080
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHIRPING)</font>

281
00:25:13.200 --> 00:25:15.370
<font color="#ff00ff">(SPACECRAFT WHIRRING)</font>

282
00:25:15.540 --> 00:25:16.950
Medical freighter.

283
00:25:18.450 --> 00:25:20.330
Pleasure barge. boring.

284
00:25:20.410 --> 00:25:21.540
<font color="#ff00ff">(SAD CHIRP)</font>

285
00:25:22.080 --> 00:25:24.080
Casino ship? Not bad.

286
00:25:24.160 --> 00:25:25.250
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHIRPS IN AGREEMENT)</font>

287
00:25:26.410 --> 00:25:28.410
Ooh. A Tri-wing. That's a new one.

288
00:25:28.500 --> 00:25:29.700
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHIRPS EXCITEDLY)</font>

289
00:25:29.790 --> 00:25:31.620
Ooh. An Aquillian Ranger.

290
00:25:31.700 --> 00:25:35.080
Probably scouting for Merson pirates.

291
00:25:35.160 --> 00:25:36.660
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHIRPS)</font>

292
00:25:36.750 --> 00:25:38.750
No? Trader. maybe?

293
00:25:38.830 --> 00:25:40.000
<font color="#138ce9">BREHA:</font> Leia Organa!

294
00:25:41.870 --> 00:25:43.620
You had to do this today?

295
00:25:43.700 --> 00:25:44.700
Do what?

296
00:25:44.790 --> 00:25:45.870
Down.

297
00:25:46.450 --> 00:25:47.950
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHIRPS NERVOUSLY)</font>

298
00:25:50.870 --> 00:25:52.790
It is like raising a Glor-ag.

299
00:25:58.700 --> 00:26:00.040
No Lola for the rest of the day.

300
00:26:00.120 --> 00:26:02.160
But she didn't do anything.

301
00:26:02.250 --> 00:26:03.250
Shut her down.

302
00:26:04.790 --> 00:26:05.870
I mean it.

303
00:26:07.910 --> 00:26:09.790
<font color="#ff00ff">(LOLA DEACTIVATES)</font>

304
00:26:12.500 --> 00:26:15.450
If you behaved as well as you climb.

305
00:26:16.000 --> 00:26:17.620
you'd be a senator already.

306
00:26:18.120 --> 00:26:19.580
<font color="#ff00ff">(SIGHS)</font>

307
00:26:19.660 --> 00:26:22.120
<font color="#ff00ff">(SIGHS)</font> You'll have to change
in the speeder. Come.

308
00:26:22.200 --> 00:26:25.620
It's not like anyone would miss me
if I wasn't there.

309
00:26:25.700 --> 00:26:26.790
I'd miss you.

310
00:26:26.870 --> 00:26:28.620
All I ever do is wave.

311
00:26:28.700 --> 00:26:30.290
<font color="#138ce9">BREHA:</font> Then do more than wave.

312
00:26:30.370 --> 00:26:32.500
You get out of this what you put into it.

313
00:26:34.250 --> 00:26:35.410
<font color="#138ce9">LEIA:</font> I'm sorry. Mother.

314
00:26:36.080 --> 00:26:37.410
I really am.

315
00:26:38.000 --> 00:26:40.290
I promise I won't do it again.

316
00:26:43.410 --> 00:26:44.830
<font color="#ff00ff">(SIGHS)</font>

317
00:26:46.200 --> 00:26:48.950
You know. I can feel you doing that.

318
00:26:49.660 --> 00:26:50.660
Come on.

319
00:26:50.750 --> 00:26:52.660
<font color="#138ce9">LEIA:</font> It's like living in a prison.

320
00:26:52.750 --> 00:26:53.830
<font color="#138ce9">BREHA:</font> A prison?

321
00:26:55.040 --> 00:26:58.040
<font color="#ff00ff">(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING)</font>

322
00:27:00.580 --> 00:27:04.620
- <font color="#ff00ff">(WHISTLE BLOWING)</font>
- <font color="#ff00ff">(WORKERS CHATTERING WEARILY)</font>

323
00:27:30.660 --> 00:27:34.290
<font color="#ff00ff">(WHOOSHING)</font>

324
00:27:38.660 --> 00:27:41.830
<font color="#ff00ff">(INDISTINCT CHATTER)</font>

325
00:27:48.830 --> 00:27:50.040
<font color="#ff00ff">(CLATTERS)</font>

326
00:27:52.290 --> 00:27:53.950
I want you to stay away from him.

327
00:27:55.250 --> 00:27:57.040
We don't need anything from you. Ben.

328
00:27:57.120 --> 00:27:58.700
It's just a toy.

329
00:27:58.790 --> 00:28:00.330
It's a lot more than that.

330
00:28:00.410 --> 00:28:03.200
There's more to life than your farm. Owen.

331
00:28:03.290 --> 00:28:06.200
He needs to see that.
There's a whole galaxy out there.

332
00:28:06.290 --> 00:28:09.580
I'm asking you to leave us alone. Ben.

333
00:28:09.660 --> 00:28:10.660
I mean it.

334
00:28:11.160 --> 00:28:12.160
Is he okay?

335
00:28:13.500 --> 00:28:15.370
You don't care if he's okay.

336
00:28:16.660 --> 00:28:18.000
You care if he's showing.

337
00:28:18.080 --> 00:28:19.790
He's my responsibility. Owen.

338
00:28:19.870 --> 00:28:21.540
- I'm his uncle.
- We talked about this.

339
00:28:21.620 --> 00:28:24.040
When the time comes. he must be trained.

340
00:28:24.120 --> 00:28:25.500
Like you trained his father?

341
00:28:27.080 --> 00:28:29.160
Anakin is dead. Ben.

342
00:28:30.750 --> 00:28:33.160
and I won't let you
make the same mistake twice.

343
00:28:34.500 --> 00:28:38.160
So. leave him on the farm with his family.
where he belongs.

344
00:28:40.790 --> 00:28:42.790
<font color="#138ce9">MAN:</font> Move. Now.

345
00:28:43.250 --> 00:28:45.160
- <font color="#ff00ff">(CROWD MURMURING)</font>
- Get back.

346
00:28:46.330 --> 00:28:47.410
All of you.

347
00:28:48.950 --> 00:28:50.040
Out of the way.

348
00:28:53.620 --> 00:28:54.790
Back up.

349
00:29:00.450 --> 00:29:02.290
You know why we are here.

350
00:29:04.120 --> 00:29:08.290
There is a Jedi hiding on this planet.

351
00:29:08.370 --> 00:29:10.910
We need to know where he is.

352
00:29:12.290 --> 00:29:13.750
You will be rewarded well.

353
00:29:13.830 --> 00:29:14.870
Or you'll be punished!

354
00:29:14.950 --> 00:29:16.000
<font color="#138ce9">FIFTH BROTHER:</font> Reva!

355
00:29:16.080 --> 00:29:17.620
Hands go first!

356
00:29:19.910 --> 00:29:22.580
That way. when you reach for anything.

357
00:29:25.200 --> 00:29:26.290
you think of us.

358
00:29:31.790 --> 00:29:33.370
<font color="#138ce9">WOMAN:</font> This is the Outer Rim.

359
00:29:34.620 --> 00:29:36.200
You have no rights here.

360
00:29:36.750 --> 00:29:38.540
We're not under the Empire's...

361
00:29:38.620 --> 00:29:41.290
- <font color="#ff00ff">(WOMAN SCREAMING)</font>
- <font color="#ff00ff">(CROWD GASPING. EXCLAIMING)</font>

362
00:29:41.370 --> 00:29:43.410
<font color="#138ce9">REVA:</font> All we want is information.

363
00:29:44.160 --> 00:29:49.910
If anyone knows anything about a Jedi...

364
00:29:55.370 --> 00:29:56.540
You know something?

365
00:30:04.370 --> 00:30:05.450
What's your name?

366
00:30:06.700 --> 00:30:07.830
Owen.

367
00:30:08.790 --> 00:30:09.870
<font color="#138ce9">REVA:</font> Owen.

368
00:30:10.290 --> 00:30:11.620
Farmer. right?

369
00:30:13.040 --> 00:30:14.040
Wife?

370
00:30:14.120 --> 00:30:15.120
Kids?

371
00:30:16.540 --> 00:30:17.950
My family's of no concern to you.

372
00:30:18.040 --> 00:30:19.330
They might be.

373
00:30:19.410 --> 00:30:22.040
- You got a Jedi on that farm. too?
- No.

374
00:30:22.120 --> 00:30:23.370
Why should I believe you?

375
00:30:23.450 --> 00:30:25.250
I have no love for the Jedi.

376
00:30:26.370 --> 00:30:27.450
Jedi are vermin.

377
00:30:28.620 --> 00:30:30.330
I kill vermin on my farm.

378
00:30:31.330 --> 00:30:32.830
You protect your family.

379
00:30:35.540 --> 00:30:36.790
I like that. Owen.

380
00:30:39.620 --> 00:30:40.620
It's important.

381
00:30:47.910 --> 00:30:50.000
You think you could protect them from me?

382
00:30:51.750 --> 00:30:52.910
<font color="#ff00ff">(SCOFFS)</font>

383
00:30:53.950 --> 00:30:59.370
<font color="#ff00ff">(SHOUTING)</font> Tell me where the Jedi is.
or this man and his family die!

384
00:30:59.450 --> 00:31:01.370
<font color="#ff00ff">(CROWD GASPING)</font>

385
00:31:02.370 --> 00:31:03.870
The Jedi are cowards.

386
00:31:05.950 --> 00:31:07.790
They failed you.

387
00:31:07.870 --> 00:31:10.620
abandoned you.

388
00:31:11.250 --> 00:31:13.910
There is no point in protecting them.

389
00:31:14.000 --> 00:31:16.040
They would not do the same for you.

390
00:31:20.620 --> 00:31:22.160
But you can save this man.

391
00:31:28.660 --> 00:31:30.290
- Save his family.
- <font color="#ff00ff">(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATES)</font>

392
00:31:30.370 --> 00:31:32.700
<font color="#ff00ff">(CROWD GASPING)</font>

393
00:31:36.580 --> 00:31:37.700
<font color="#138ce9">FIFTH BROTHER:</font> Enough!

394
00:31:39.450 --> 00:31:41.290
If you remember anything.

395
00:31:41.830 --> 00:31:43.410
rewards will be given.

396
00:31:45.910 --> 00:31:47.910
Stand down. Third Sister.

397
00:31:50.160 --> 00:31:51.250
Now!

398
00:31:52.410 --> 00:31:53.620
<font color="#ff00ff">(LIGHTSABER DEACTIVATES)</font>

399
00:31:53.700 --> 00:31:55.120
Next time. Owen.

400
00:31:58.200 --> 00:32:01.450
<font color="#ff00ff">(CROWD MURMURING)</font>

401
00:32:01.540 --> 00:32:03.120
<font color="#138ce9">FIFTH BROTHER:</font> Ah! Move.

402
00:32:03.950 --> 00:32:07.750
<font color="#ff00ff">(BREATHING HEAVILY)</font>

403
00:32:10.540 --> 00:32:11.700
<font color="#ff00ff">(BOTH GRUNT)</font>

404
00:32:12.200 --> 00:32:15.160
You are too impulsive.

405
00:32:15.750 --> 00:32:17.250
I'm sick of wasting time!

406
00:32:18.000 --> 00:32:19.660
This place is beneath us!

407
00:32:20.250 --> 00:32:22.000
The Grand Inquisitor was right.

408
00:32:23.540 --> 00:32:25.080
You still want Kenobi.

409
00:32:26.950 --> 00:32:30.080
But he's gone. and you won't find him.

410
00:32:30.870 --> 00:32:33.450
We spent the last ten years
looking for him.

411
00:32:35.120 --> 00:32:37.450
Maybe you've been looking
in the wrong places.

412
00:32:38.330 --> 00:32:41.750
What is it you think you will gain
by capturing him?

413
00:32:43.120 --> 00:32:44.330
What I'm owed.

414
00:32:49.660 --> 00:32:51.580
Be careful. Third Sister.

415
00:32:51.660 --> 00:32:53.410
You go too far.

416
00:32:55.290 --> 00:32:57.040
Maybe you don't go far enough.

417
00:33:00.410 --> 00:33:03.410
- <font color="#ff00ff">(WHOOSHING)</font>
- <font color="#ff00ff">(CROWD MURMURING)</font>

418
00:33:08.080 --> 00:33:09.120
Thank you. Owen.

419
00:33:09.580 --> 00:33:10.700
<font color="#ff00ff">(SCOFFS)</font>

420
00:33:15.410 --> 00:33:16.870
I didn't do it for you.

421
00:33:27.700 --> 00:33:30.200
<font color="#ff00ff">(WHOOSHING)</font>

422
00:33:54.160 --> 00:33:56.000
Right on time as always.

423
00:33:56.080 --> 00:33:57.410
Anything good today?

424
00:33:57.500 --> 00:33:59.950
A trade ship and an Aquillian Ranger.

425
00:34:00.040 --> 00:34:01.790
Probably scouring for pirates.

426
00:34:01.870 --> 00:34:03.410
That's what I said.

427
00:34:03.500 --> 00:34:05.370
- Don't encourage her.
- All right.

428
00:34:08.660 --> 00:34:09.870
Come now.

429
00:34:09.950 --> 00:34:11.580
Let's get this over with.

430
00:34:14.750 --> 00:34:16.790
<font color="#ff00ff">(LIVELY CHATTER)</font>

431
00:34:16.870 --> 00:34:18.040
- Breha.
- Sister.

432
00:34:18.120 --> 00:34:19.370
- <font color="#138ce9">BAIL:</font> Greetings.
- <font color="#138ce9">LEIA:</font> Hi. cousin.

433
00:34:24.330 --> 00:34:25.370
<font color="#138ce9">MAN:</font> Princess.

434
00:34:25.450 --> 00:34:27.790
- <font color="#138ce9">WOMAN:</font> Oh. there they are. <font color="#ff00ff">(LAUGHS)</font>
- <font color="#ff00ff">(CROWD CHEERING)</font>

435
00:34:27.870 --> 00:34:29.040
<font color="#138ce9">MAN 2:</font> Princess.

436
00:34:30.080 --> 00:34:31.410
<font color="#138ce9">MAN 3:</font> Hi. Princess.

437
00:34:40.290 --> 00:34:42.790
<font color="#ff00ff">(LIVELY CHATTER)</font>

438
00:34:43.700 --> 00:34:45.040
<font color="#138ce9">KAYO:</font> Profits have been good.

439
00:34:45.910 --> 00:34:50.950
After the disaster of the Republic.
the Empire is finally lining some pockets.

440
00:34:51.040 --> 00:34:53.750
There are still some issues
that we need to address.

441
00:34:54.330 --> 00:34:56.790
Slave labor. taxation of the Outer Rim...

442
00:34:56.870 --> 00:34:59.370
I didn't come here to end slavery. Bail.

443
00:35:00.040 --> 00:35:01.750
I came to eat your food. <font color="#ff00ff">(CHUCKLES)</font>

444
00:35:02.540 --> 00:35:04.200
Save the bleeding heart for the Senate.

445
00:35:04.910 --> 00:35:06.830
A drink. Senator?

446
00:35:06.910 --> 00:35:07.950
<font color="#ff00ff">(SIGHS)</font>

447
00:35:08.410 --> 00:35:10.120
- Ah. Thank you.
- <font color="#ff00ff">(ALIEN SPEAKING OTHER LANGUAGE)</font>

448
00:35:10.200 --> 00:35:12.450
<font color="#ff00ff">(C-3PO TRANSLATING IN OTHER LANGUAGE)</font>

449
00:35:14.000 --> 00:35:15.080
<font color="#138ce9">Y-O:</font> Your Highness.

450
00:35:15.370 --> 00:35:16.790
Oh. Thanks. Y-O.

451
00:35:16.870 --> 00:35:17.950
<font color="#138ce9">Y-O:</font> My pleasure.

452
00:35:19.120 --> 00:35:20.330
<font color="#ff00ff">(SCOFFS)</font> You thank your droids?

453
00:35:20.950 --> 00:35:22.450
It's good manners.

454
00:35:22.540 --> 00:35:25.450
You don't need manners
when you're talking to a lower life form.

455
00:35:25.540 --> 00:35:28.700
Then I guess I don't need manners
when I'm talking to you.

456
00:35:29.080 --> 00:35:30.080
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHUCKLES)</font>

457
00:35:31.000 --> 00:35:33.580
You know the difference
between you and me. cousin?

458
00:35:34.290 --> 00:35:35.290
I know things.

459
00:35:35.870 --> 00:35:38.450
My father says
they never let you leave this planet.

460
00:35:39.660 --> 00:35:43.250
They don't want anybody to know about you
because you're not one of us.

461
00:35:44.290 --> 00:35:45.790
You're not even a real Organa.

462
00:35:47.830 --> 00:35:48.950
<font color="#ff00ff">(SCOFFS)</font>

463
00:35:50.500 --> 00:35:51.910
You're scared of him.

464
00:35:53.120 --> 00:35:56.660
Your father. You want him to like you.
so you repeat what he says

465
00:35:56.750 --> 00:35:59.160
even though you don't really know
what it means.

466
00:36:00.040 --> 00:36:02.830
You think being like him
will make people frightened of you.

467
00:36:02.910 --> 00:36:05.580
but really. you're the one who's scared.

468
00:36:05.660 --> 00:36:08.410
You've never made one decision
for yourself in your entire life.

469
00:36:08.500 --> 00:36:10.200
and you never will.

470
00:36:11.040 --> 00:36:13.830
I may not have seen much. cousin.

471
00:36:15.000 --> 00:36:16.250
but I can see that.

472
00:36:22.750 --> 00:36:24.660
He was being horrible to everyone.

473
00:36:24.750 --> 00:36:25.870
He's your cousin.

474
00:36:25.950 --> 00:36:27.450
He's rude to droids.

475
00:36:27.540 --> 00:36:29.790
You have to rise above. Leia.

476
00:36:32.540 --> 00:36:33.870
You owe him an apology.

477
00:36:34.330 --> 00:36:37.290
I'd rather be digested by a jakobeast.

478
00:36:49.120 --> 00:36:53.540
<font color="#138ce9">BAIL:</font> I wanted to live out way past Kathou
when I was your age.

479
00:36:54.500 --> 00:36:57.330
Chase purrgil. you know?

480
00:36:57.410 --> 00:36:58.910
I had a whole plan.

481
00:37:00.700 --> 00:37:01.700
What happened?

482
00:37:02.450 --> 00:37:03.540
I got older.

483
00:37:04.410 --> 00:37:06.450
Had to find some other adventures.

484
00:37:07.450 --> 00:37:09.200
Started chasing your mother instead.

485
00:37:12.000 --> 00:37:13.660
This is your future. Leia.

486
00:37:14.450 --> 00:37:17.450
In a few years. you'll be
off to university. then Junior Senate.

487
00:37:17.540 --> 00:37:18.540
<font color="#138ce9">LEIA:</font> The Senate's boring.

488
00:37:18.620 --> 00:37:21.040
It's people in itchy clothes arguing.

489
00:37:21.120 --> 00:37:24.040
<font color="#ff00ff">(LAUGHING)</font> Well. it may seem so...

490
00:37:24.120 --> 00:37:25.370
I don't want to be a senator.

491
00:37:25.910 --> 00:37:28.580
It is why
you'll probably be one of the best.

492
00:37:29.790 --> 00:37:31.750
I'm not even a real Organa.

493
00:37:32.660 --> 00:37:33.660
What?

494
00:37:38.410 --> 00:37:39.410
Don't ever say that.

495
00:37:41.540 --> 00:37:42.700
You are our child.

496
00:37:44.120 --> 00:37:48.250
You are an Organa in every way.

497
00:37:50.370 --> 00:37:52.660
One day. this planet
will look to you. Leia.

498
00:37:54.910 --> 00:37:56.410
There are many ways to lead.

499
00:37:56.500 --> 00:37:58.750
You just have to find yours.

500
00:37:58.830 --> 00:38:01.500
Plus. imagine the look
on your cousin's face

501
00:38:01.580 --> 00:38:03.660
when you get to boss him around for real.

502
00:38:04.410 --> 00:38:05.410
<font color="#ff00ff">(BOTH LAUGH)</font>

503
00:38:07.700 --> 00:38:08.790
But for now.

504
00:38:10.660 --> 00:38:11.750
we will...

505
00:38:13.540 --> 00:38:14.700
apologize.

506
00:38:15.660 --> 00:38:16.660
Yes. Father.

507
00:38:16.750 --> 00:38:17.750
Hmm.

508
00:38:22.660 --> 00:38:24.160
I'll wait for you downstairs.

509
00:38:25.790 --> 00:38:26.830
<font color="#ff00ff">(LEIA SIGHS)</font>

510
00:38:40.580 --> 00:38:41.660
Thank you.

511
00:38:42.250 --> 00:38:43.330
She's gone.

512
00:38:43.540 --> 00:38:45.750
I thought you said
you've really got through to her.

513
00:38:46.250 --> 00:38:47.410
You know what she's like.

514
00:38:47.500 --> 00:38:48.910
I know who she's like.

515
00:38:49.660 --> 00:38:50.830
Send a unit.

516
00:38:50.910 --> 00:38:51.910
She can't be far.

517
00:38:59.330 --> 00:39:00.950
<font color="#138ce9">VECT:</font> Hello. Princess.

518
00:39:03.160 --> 00:39:04.330
Why are you here?

519
00:39:05.370 --> 00:39:06.450
Just waiting.

520
00:39:06.910 --> 00:39:08.250
For what?

521
00:39:08.910 --> 00:39:10.250
For you.

522
00:39:10.620 --> 00:39:11.700
<font color="#ff00ff">(GASPS)</font>

523
00:39:13.580 --> 00:39:15.700
<font color="#ff00ff">(LEIA PANTING)</font>

524
00:39:21.870 --> 00:39:24.080
<font color="#ff00ff">(ALL PANTING)</font>

525
00:39:29.950 --> 00:39:30.950
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTING)</font>

526
00:39:34.080 --> 00:39:35.120
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTS)</font>

527
00:39:35.790 --> 00:39:37.040
<font color="#ff00ff">(SHOUTING)</font>

528
00:39:45.870 --> 00:39:46.910
<font color="#ff00ff">(GROANS)</font>

529
00:39:51.200 --> 00:39:52.290
<font color="#138ce9">LEIA:</font> Help!

530
00:39:53.750 --> 00:39:54.830
Help!

531
00:39:54.910 --> 00:39:56.160
<font color="#ff00ff">(PANTING)</font>

532
00:39:56.250 --> 00:39:57.830
Help! Help me. please!

533
00:39:58.410 --> 00:39:59.500
<font color="#ff00ff">(GROANS)</font>

534
00:40:00.200 --> 00:40:02.410
<font color="#ff00ff">(PANTING)</font>

535
00:40:09.750 --> 00:40:12.910
<font color="#ff00ff">(DEVICE BEEPING)</font>

536
00:40:37.290 --> 00:40:38.870
<i>We don't know who it was.</i>

537
00:40:38.950 --> 00:40:40.580
<i>No ransom. no leads.</i>

538
00:40:41.910 --> 00:40:46.040
<i>Whoever they are.
they knew where she would be. They...</i>

539
00:40:46.750 --> 00:40:47.830
<i>They were waiting.</i>

540
00:40:47.910 --> 00:40:48.910
<font color="#ff00ff">(CLEARS THROAT)</font>

541
00:40:49.200 --> 00:40:51.120
<i>She needs you. Obi-Wan.</i>

542
00:40:52.160 --> 00:40:53.660
<i>We can't trust anyone else.</i>

543
00:40:55.830 --> 00:40:57.250
What about the Senate?

544
00:40:57.750 --> 00:40:59.500
<font color="#138ce9">BAIL:</font> <i>We cannot let this become public.</i>

545
00:41:00.160 --> 00:41:01.910
<i>It would draw too much attention.</i>

546
00:41:02.750 --> 00:41:05.660
Well. your guard then? Or a bounty hunter?

547
00:41:05.750 --> 00:41:09.830
<i>Only you know how important
she really is. Obi-Wan.</i>

548
00:41:09.910 --> 00:41:11.500
<i>If Leia is discovered...</i>

549
00:41:11.580 --> 00:41:13.160
I can't leave here. Bail.

550
00:41:14.370 --> 00:41:15.540
My duty is to the boy...

551
00:41:15.620 --> 00:41:17.540
<i>What about your duty to his sister?</i>

552
00:41:19.370 --> 00:41:21.200
<i>She's as important as he is.</i>

553
00:41:23.580 --> 00:41:24.950
<font color="#ff00ff">(SIGHS)</font>

554
00:41:27.410 --> 00:41:28.910
It's been ten years.

555
00:41:32.620 --> 00:41:34.040
I'm not who I used to be.

556
00:41:40.160 --> 00:41:41.250
Find someone else.

557
00:41:42.870 --> 00:41:44.040
She'll be better off.

558
00:41:45.370 --> 00:41:47.290
<font color="#ff00ff">(WHOOSHING)</font>

559
00:41:47.790 --> 00:41:50.250
<font color="#138ce9">LEIA:</font> <font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTING)</font> Let go of me!

560
00:41:50.330 --> 00:41:51.790
- Let go!
- Shut her up.

561
00:41:52.500 --> 00:41:54.830
<font color="#ff00ff">(MERCENARY AND LEIA GRUNTING)</font>

562
00:41:56.950 --> 00:42:02.000
<font color="#ff00ff">(MERCENARY LAUGHING MANIACALLY)</font>

563
00:42:03.500 --> 00:42:05.700
- <font color="#ff00ff">(WHISTLE BLOWS)</font>
- <font color="#ff00ff">(WORKERS CHATTERING)</font>

564
00:42:26.830 --> 00:42:29.830
<font color="#ff00ff">(CROWD GASPING. MURMURING)</font>

565
00:42:58.120 --> 00:42:59.870
<font color="#ff00ff">(MAN SOBBING)</font>

566
00:43:10.870 --> 00:43:13.080
<font color="#ff00ff">(WHIRRING)</font>

567
00:43:37.250 --> 00:43:38.830
<font color="#138ce9">BAIL:</font> She's headed for Daiyu.

568
00:43:41.000 --> 00:43:42.750
You should not have come.

569
00:43:43.700 --> 00:43:46.080
They hid their signature
behind a freight transport.

570
00:43:46.160 --> 00:43:48.000
The ship is on its way there now.

571
00:43:48.750 --> 00:43:49.790
I can't.

572
00:43:49.870 --> 00:43:51.620
She's my daughter. Obi-Wan.

573
00:43:51.700 --> 00:43:52.870
I told you...

574
00:43:53.950 --> 00:43:55.410
I'm not the man you remember.

575
00:43:55.500 --> 00:43:56.830
You're going to have to be!

576
00:43:56.910 --> 00:43:58.040
I can't leave the boy.

577
00:43:58.120 --> 00:44:00.040
This isn't about the boy. and you know it!

578
00:44:01.160 --> 00:44:03.120
You've made mistakes. We all did.

579
00:44:03.200 --> 00:44:04.450
It's the past.

580
00:44:05.410 --> 00:44:06.910
Move on. Be done with it.

581
00:44:07.950 --> 00:44:09.620
You couldn't save Anakin.

582
00:44:11.580 --> 00:44:12.910
but you can save her.

583
00:44:15.540 --> 00:44:16.790
And what if I can't?

584
00:44:19.160 --> 00:44:22.080
There is no one
I trust more with my child than you.

585
00:44:23.950 --> 00:44:26.660
Please. old friend.

586
00:44:28.410 --> 00:44:29.500
For her.

587
00:44:30.870 --> 00:44:32.120
One last fight.

588
00:44:38.580 --> 00:44:39.950
<font color="#ff00ff">(WHOOSHING)</font>

589
00:44:41.830 --> 00:44:44.910
Come on. Lola. Come on.

590
00:44:47.040 --> 00:44:48.910
<font color="#ff00ff">(LOLA ACTIVATES)</font>

591
00:44:51.750 --> 00:44:54.700
<font color="#ff00ff">(LOLA CHIRPING)</font>

592
00:44:55.000 --> 00:44:56.870
<font color="#ff00ff">(SHUSHING)</font>

593
00:44:58.620 --> 00:45:00.120
Can you untie me?

594
00:45:05.330 --> 00:45:06.870
<font color="#ff00ff">(DOOR OPENS)</font>

595
00:45:08.450 --> 00:45:10.160
I'm not afraid of you.

596
00:45:10.410 --> 00:45:11.450
<font color="#ff00ff">(SCOFFS)</font>

597
00:45:12.250 --> 00:45:13.410
Give it time.

598
00:45:14.790 --> 00:45:16.870
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHIRPING)</font>

599
00:45:19.290 --> 00:45:20.410
Lola!

600
00:45:20.500 --> 00:45:21.700
<font color="#ff00ff">(LOLA DEACTIVATES)</font>

601
00:45:21.790 --> 00:45:24.080
My father will rescue me!

602
00:45:24.160 --> 00:45:26.120
He'll send a whole army!

603
00:45:26.700 --> 00:45:28.540
No one's coming for you.

604
00:45:35.330 --> 00:45:37.540
<font color="#ff00ff">(DOOR CLOSING)</font>

605
00:45:50.080 --> 00:45:52.000
<font color="#ff00ff">(EOPIE GRUNTING)</font>

606
00:46:22.620 --> 00:46:24.370
<font color="#ff00ff">(LEIA GRUNTING)</font>

607
00:46:25.620 --> 00:46:26.870
This is a bad idea.

608
00:46:27.620 --> 00:46:28.700
Kidnapping kids...

609
00:46:30.330 --> 00:46:31.500
you think it's gonna work?

610
00:46:32.080 --> 00:46:33.500
Just get this over with.

611
00:46:37.080 --> 00:46:38.120
<font color="#ff00ff">(SYSTEM BEEPS)</font>

612
00:47:14.330 --> 00:47:15.660
You sure he's gonna come?

613
00:47:16.540 --> 00:47:18.700
<font color="#138ce9">REVA:</font> <i>He fought beside her father
during the war.</i>

614
00:47:19.660 --> 00:47:20.750
<i>He'll come.</i>

615
00:47:21.750 --> 00:47:23.250
<i>He won't be able to help it.</i>

616
00:47:24.450 --> 00:47:26.700
<i>The Jedi will hunt himself.</i>

617
00:47:29.500 --> 00:47:32.500
<font color="#ff00ff">(INDISTINCT CHATTER
IN OTHER LANGUAGE ON PA)</font>

618
00:47:53.910 --> 00:47:55.370
Well?

619
00:47:55.450 --> 00:47:56.620
You coming or not?

620
00:47:56.620 --> 00:48:11.620
